{"tid":2143691,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美國筆會：荷李活為中共自我審查","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T14:21:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e62042bff741c72f77ae97e6f95132f6e577a3","tid":2143691,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200807/3JNLBLVAENIHPVAK2JQQMRWIEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200807%2F3JNLBLVAENIHPVAK2JQQMRWIEI%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLBPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=99a3c95b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200807%2F3JNLBLVAENIHPVAK2JQQMRWIEI%2F&h=bd629c37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200807/3JNLBLVAENIHPVAK2JQQMRWIEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美國筆會：荷李活為中共自我審查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tcV2mMOv7cvelOU_FzHNdbBJ09w=/640x443/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WEDRDGQHU2BVWNW4TREL62BSKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtcV2mMOv7cvelOU_FzHNdbBJ09w%3D%2F640x443%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWEDRDGQHU2BVWNW4TREL62BSKU.jpg&h=e226065b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《屈機起格命》（左）及《赤色黎明》（右）等荷李活電影都為迎合中共而自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n反審查團體美國筆會。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：回絕北京利誘 索馬利蘭拒與台斷交<br />\n<br />\n「中共正塑造全球觀眾」<br />\n<br />\n1922年已設立的美國筆會在當地時間5日發表長達94頁的報告，題為《荷李活製作，北京審查：美國影業和中國政府影響力》，主要撰寫人表示中國的審查已不安於只針對自己的本土製作，壓縮中國境內的異議、獨立思想和創造力，近年在中國「龐大的經濟刺激下，中國審查制度的長臂也深入到荷李活，塑造觀念、灌輸敏感這樣的概念，並重塑『可以』及『不可以』被呈現的內容界限。」內文指出，西藏、台灣、香港政治和新疆等敏感議題完全碰不得。<br />\n<br />\n美國筆會表示，在有可能被中國打入黑名單等報復措施之下，荷李活製作人甚至開始審查那些並非要為打入中國市場的電影，以免影響其他會在中國大陸上映的電影企劃。報告中提到，男星李察基爾（Richard Gere）主演過描述中國司法系統腐敗的電影《紅色角落》（Red Corner），現實生活中也頻為西藏人權發聲，荷李活製作人怕激怒中國，根本不敢找他拍片。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中央廣播電台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TIRBCK7CW7F2FhOJ-ShpnRgDpCg=/556x711/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WSC6XF2HZ26FSDBNDFNVFCE5CU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTIRBCK7CW7F2FhOJ-ShpnRgDpCg%3D%2F556x711%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWSC6XF2HZ26FSDBNDFNVFCE5CU.gif&h=66f2d693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d119cc0d9cd158d44ecf248c7725af7dcea2750","tid":2143691,"uid":236359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"有反人類特色的假社會主義小氣國"},{"pid":"d0ed706d61cdbbdbdd51902bfe57d98a1ab3d753","tid":2143691,"uid":284699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:52:01.000Z","msg":"同性戀其實唔少地方都唔受<br />\n攞刪同性戀做例子就太濫<br />\n明明仲有好多奶共電影做例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc64cf1cf0eb509e163603f208ff47083aeb45c","tid":2143691,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"仲有唉人man3<br />\n滿大人變左鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1707019258c6c922429f765d7801789a5f014a24","tid":2143691,"uid":244113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"荷里活同迪士尼奶共都唔係第一日"},{"pid":"b7a09438bbcfd6bbbd01b5781e74cb56fc0e4c3e","tid":2143691,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dc64cf1cf0eb509e163603f208ff47083aeb45c","tid":2143691,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"仲有唉人man3<br />\n滿大人變左鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:23:50.000Z","msg":"而家咪搵咗梁朝偉做真身囉<br />\n即刻俾班小粉紅屌辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df477eac92fd3c9c46a683f2f7e39665e2721b22","tid":2143691,"uid":322685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"BoRhap嗰個係唔cut唔俾上映 <br />\n都叫自我審查咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迎合嗰到啲觀眾姐<br />\nInside Out美國同日本版都有唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}